\c 7
\s Vana vaIsakari
\p
\v 1 Vanakomana vaIsakari: Tora, naPua, naJashubhi, naShimironi, ivo vana.
\v 2 Vanakomana vaTora: Uzi, naRefaya, naJerieri, naJamai, naIbhisami, naShemueri, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, idzo dzaTora; vaiva varume vane simba noumhare pakati pamarudzi avo, pamazuva aDhavhidhi vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri namazana matanhatu.
\p
\v 3 Vanakomana vaUzi; Izirahiya; navanakomana vaIzirahiya: Mikaeri naObhadhiya, naJoeri, naIshia, ivo vashanu; ava vose vakange vari vakuru.
\v 4 Kwavari, kumarudzi avo nokudzimba dzamadzibaba avo, kwakange kuna mapoka ehondo dzokurwa ane zviuru zvina makumi matatu nezvitanhatu; nekuti vakange vana vakadzi vazhinji navanakomana vazhinji.
\p
\v 5 Hama dzavo pakati pedzimba dzose dzaIsakari, ivo varume vane simba noumhare, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi masere nezvinomwe, kana vachiverengwa mazita avo ose.
\s Vana vaBhenjamini naNafutari
\p
\v 6 Vanakomana vaBhenjamini: Bhera, naBhekeri, naJedhiyaeri, ivo vatatu.
\v 7 Vanakomana vaBhera: Ezibhoni, naUzi, naUzieri, naJerimoti, naIri, ivo vashanu. Ivo vakange vari vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, varume vane simba noumhare, vakaverengwa mazita avo vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri namakumi matatu navana.
\p
\v 8 Vanakomana vaBhekeri: Zemira, naJoashi, naEriezeri, naErioenai, naOmiri, naJeremoti, naAbhiia, naAnatoti, naArimeti. Ivo vose vakange vari vanakomana vaBhekeri.
\v 9 Vakaverengwa mazita avo namarudzi avo, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, varume vane simba noumhare, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri namazana maviri.
\p
\v 10 Vanakomana vaJedhiyaeri: Bhirihani, navanakomana vaBhirihani; Jehushi, naBhenjamini, naEhudhi, naKenani, naZetani, naTarishishi, naAhishahari.
\p
\v 11 Ivo vose vakange vari vanakomana vaJedhiyaeri, vachiverengwa vakuru vedzimba dzamamdzibaba avo, varume vane simba noumhare, vakasvika zviuru zvine gumi nezvinomwe namazana maviri, vakange vachigona kuenda kuhondo kundorwa.
\v 12 NaShupimiwo, naHupimi, vanakomana vaIri, naHushimi, vanakomana vaAheri.
\p
\v 13 Vanakomana vaNafutari: Jazieri, naGuni, naJezeri, naSharumi, vanakomana vaBhiriha.
\s Vana vaManase
\p
\v 14 Vanakomana vaManase: Asirieri, waakaberekerwa nomukadzi wake; (murongo wake muArami akabereka Makiri baba vaGiriyadhi;
\v 15 Makiri akawana mukadzi worudzi rwaHupimi naShupimi, zita rehanzvadzi yake raiva Maaka;) zita rowechipiri rakange riri Zerofehadhi; Zerofehadhi akange anavakunda.
\p
\v 16 Maaka mukadzi waMakiri akabereka mwanakomana, akatumidza zita rake Pereshi; zita romunin'ina wake raiva Shereshi, vanakomana vake vakange vari Urami naRakemi.
\v 17 Vanakomana vaUrami: Bhedhani. Ndivo vanakomana vaGiriyadhi mwanakomana waMakiri, mwanakomana waManase.
\p
\v 18 Hanzvadzi yake Hamoreketi akabereka Ishodhi, naAbhiezeri, naMara.
\p
\v 19 Vanakomana vaShemidha: Ahiani, naShekemu, naRiki naAniami.
\s Vana vaEfuremu
\p
\v 20 Vanakomana vaEfuremu: Shutera, naBheredhi mwanakomana wake, naTahati mwanakomana wake, naEreadha mwanakomana wake, naTahati mwanakomana wake,
\v 21 naZabhadhi mwanakomana wake, naShutera mwanakomana wake, naEzeri, naEreadhi; ivo vakaurawa navanhu veGati vakange vakaberekerwa panyika iyo, nekuti vakange vaburukira kwavari kuzotora zvipfuwo zvavo.
\v 22 Efuremu baba vavo akavachema mazuva mazhinji, hama dzake dzikauya kuzomubata ruoko.
\v 23 Akapinda kumukadzi wake, iye akava nemimba, akabereka mwanakomana, akamutumidza zita rinonzi Bheriya; nekuti imba yake yakange ichitambudzika.
\p
\v 24 Mukunda wake waiva Sheera, iye akavaka Bhetihoroni rezasi nerokumusoro, neUzenisheera.
\p
\v 25 Mwanakomana waEfuremu aiva Refa, naReshefi, naTera mwanakomana wake, naTahani mwanakomana wake;
\v 26 naRadhani mwanakomana wake, naErishama mwanakomana wake,
\v 27 naNuni mwanakomana wake, naJoshua mwanakomana wake.
\v 28 Nyika yavo nokwavakange vagere ndiBhetieri nemisha yaro; nokumabvazuva, Naarani, nokumavirira Gezeri nemisha yaro; neShekemu nemisha yaro, kusvikira paAza nemisha yaro;
\v 29 nokumiganhu yavana vaManase. Bhetisheani nemisha yaro, neTaanaki nemisha yaro, neMegidho nemisha yaro, neDhori nemisha yaro.
\p Vana vaJosefa mwanakomana waIsraeri vakagara mumisha iyi.
\s Vanakomana vaAsheri
\p
\v 30 Vanakomana vaAsheri: Imina, naIshivha, naIshivhi, naBheriya, naSera hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 31 Vanakomana vaBheriya: Hebheri, naMarikieri, waiva baba vaBhirizaiti.
\v 32 Hebheri akabereka Jafureti, naShomeri, naHotami, naShua hanzvadzi yavo.
\v 33 Vanakomana Jafureti: Pasaki, naBhimari, naAshivati. Ndivo vanakomana vaJafureti.
\p
\v 34 Vanakomana vaShemeri: Ahi, naRoga, naJehubha, naArami.
\p
\v 35 Vanakomana vaHeremi munin'ina wake: Zofa, naImina, naShereshi, naAmari.
\p
\v 36 Vanakomana vaZofa: Shua, naHarineferi, naShuari, naBheri, naImira;
\v 37 naBheseri, naHodhi, naShama, naShirisha, naItirani, naBheera.
\p
\v 38 Vanakomana vaJeteri: Jefune, naPisipa, naAra.
\v 39 Vanakomana vaUra: Ara, naHanieri, naRizia.
\p
\v 40 Ava vose vaiva vana vaAsheri, vari vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, varume vakange vakatsaurwa, vane simba noumhare, vakuru vamachinda. Vakaverengwa namazita avo, ivo vaigona kurwa, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezvitanhatu.
